OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FTwo teenagers have been arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with an arson attack at a
OL,9,Fsynagogue in Harrow, the Deputy
OL,10,FCommissioner of the Metropolitan
OL,11,FPolice Service has said.
OL,13,FA "bottle with some sort of accelerant
OL,14,Fhad been thrown through the window" at
OL,15,FKenton United Synagogue at around
OL,16,Fmidnight on Sunday, a spokesperson for
OL,17,Fthe Met police previously said.
OL,26,@uD@COUvD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
