PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FThe Community Security Trust (CST)
OL,8,Fsaid that minor smoke damage to an
OL,9,Finternal room was caused but said no
OL,10,Fthere were injuries or significant
OL,11,Fstructural damage.
OL,13,FDeputy Commissioner Matt Jukes told
OL,14,Fthe Today programme on Monday morning
OL,15,Fthat a 17-year-old boy and 19-year-old
OL,16,Fman had been arrested in connection
OL,17,Fwith the incident.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FHe said: "I'm really pleased to say
OL,8,Fthat overnight, we have news of two
OL,9,Farrests in relation to that incident,
OL,10,F17 and 19-year-old males.
OL,12,F"We've made over the last weeks, 15
OL,13,Farrests in relation to a series of six
OL,14,Fincidents that have targeted Jewish
OL,15,Fpremises, the Jewish led ambulance
OL,16,Fservice and a Persian media
OL,17,Forganisation."
OL,19,FYehuda Black, the synagogue's rabbi,
OL,20,Fsaid the item was thrown into the
OL,21,Fmedical room.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
