PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FChief Rabbi Sir Ephraim Mirvis
OL,8,Fdescribed the arson attack as
OL,9,F"cowardly" and said "a sustained
OL,10,Fcampaign of violence and intimidation
OL,11,Fagainst the Jewish community of the UK
OL,12,Fis gathering momentum".
OL,14,FHis statement shared on X said: "This
OL,15,Fsustained attack on our community's
OL,16,Fability to worship and live in safety
OL,17,Fis an attack on the values that bind
OL,18,Fus all together."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]qD@UOUtD@VO]vD@aOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
