FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FThe attack comes as counter-terror
OL,8,Fpolice announced they are looking into
OL,9,Fwhether the series of arson attacks
OL,10,Fagainst Jewish sites in north London
OL,11,Fhave been carried out by Iranian
OL,12,Fproxies.
OL,14,FVicki Evans, deputy assistant
OL,15,Fcommissioner of the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice, previously said the incidents
OL,17,Fhave been "similar in nature",
OL,18,Ftargeting Israeli and Jewish premises
OL,19,Fwithin London.
OL,26,@yD@KOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FMs Evans said most have been claimed
OL,8,Fonline by Harakat Ashab al-Yamin al-
OL,9,FIslamia, the Islamic Movement of the
OL,10,FCompanions of the Right, which has
OL,11,Frecently claimed attacks across Europe.
OL,13,FVideo that appears to be published by
OL,14,Fthe group, also known as Hayi, shows a
OL,15,Fperson in dark clothing lighting an
OL,16,Fitem and throwing it at the Kenton
OL,17,FUnited Synagogue before running away.
OL,19,FIt was filmed by another person behind
OL,20,Fthe metal fence surrounding the
OL,21,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
