FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776690659
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested over arson attack
OL,4,Cat Kenton United Synagogue in north
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,8,Fsaid he is "appalled by recent
OL,9,Fattempted antisemitic arson attacks in
OL,10,FNorth London".
OL,12,FHe added in his statement on X,
OL,13,Fformerly Twitter: "This is abhorrent
OL,14,Fand it will not be tolerated. Attacks
OL,15,Fon our Jewish community are attacks on
OL,16,FBritain."
